	<article id="post-2516" class="post-2516 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-civil-liberties category-gaddafi category-intelligence category-law category-libya category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-politics category-shayler category-spies category-syria category-tv category-war-2 category-whistleblowers tag-abby-martin tag-gaddafi tag-intelligence-2 tag-libya tag-mi5 tag-mi6 tag-rt tag-spies-2 tag-syria tag-war tag-whistleblowers-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/04/interview-on-the-abby-martin-show-rt-america.html" title="Permalink to Interview on the Abby Martin show, RT America" rel="bookmark">Interview on the Abby Martin show, <span class="caps">RT</span> America</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/04/interview-on-the-abby-martin-show-rt-america.html" title="18:00" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-04-28T18:00:52+00:00" pubdate>April 28, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/04/interview-on-the-abby-martin-show-rt-america.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My recent inter­view on “Break­ing the Set”, Abby Martin’s show on <span class="caps">RT</span> Amer­ica, dis­cuss­ing all things whis­tleblow­ing:<br />
<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/64811132" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/64811132">Secret Agent Turns Whis­tleblower</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="http://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/04/interview-on-the-abby-martin-show-rt-america.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
